<div>
    <h1>Returns and Warranty Policy</h1>
    <h3>A refund may be issued for a purchase provided the following criteria are met:</h3>
    <ol>
        <li>The products purchased are displaying signs of manufacturing faults (not user negligence) within 24-hours from time of purchase.              </li><li>Faulty products must be returned (in original packaging) to a staff member in exchange for either a product replacement or store credit.              </li><li>In the event a customer “changes their mind” on a purchase a full financial refund can be issued provided goods have not already been delivered to the customer by a member of staff.</li></ol></div>